The paper discusses the deployment of a high capacity 4G-WiMAX network in Ghana, which involves wireless communication systems and broadband wireless access. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture). The paper also discusses the simulation of Bit-Error-Rate (BER) and the radiation pattern of the antenna, which falls under the categories of cs.IT (Information Theory) and cs.CR (Cryptography and Security). The paper also mentions multimedia services, which falls under the category of cs.MM (Multimedia). Finally, the paper discusses the design issue of planning high capacity networks in the presence of multiple interferences, which falls under the category of cs.COM (Computer Science and Game Theory).
